title: Lahiri takes tough lesson from Presidents Cup
text: Photo: Lee Jin-man, AP International team player Anirban Lahiri of India reacts on the 18th green after missing a putt to lose his match against United States' Chris Kirk in their singles match at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. International team player Anirban Lahiri of India reacts on the... INCHEON, South Korea (AP) — Anirban Lahiri was seconds away from being the star in a dream debut at the Presidents Cup.
